32#include <core/client.h>

39static bool
40nv40_fifo_dma_engine(struct nvkm_engine *engine, u32 *reg, u32 *ctx)
41{
42 switch (engine->subdev.index) {
43 case NVKM_ENGINE_DMAOBJ:
44 case NVKM_ENGINE_SW:
45 return false;
46 case NVKM_ENGINE_GR:
47 *reg = 0x0032e0;
48 *ctx = 0x38;
49 return true;
50 case NVKM_ENGINE_MPEG:
51 *reg = 0x00330c;
52 *ctx = 0x54;
53 return true;
54 default:
55 WARN_ON(1);
56 return false;
57 }
58}
59
60static int
61nv40_fifo_dma_engine_fini(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base,
62 struct nvkm_engine *engine, bool suspend)
63{
64 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
65 struct nv04_fifo *fifo = chan->fifo;
66 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->base.engine.subdev.device;
67 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = device->imem;
68 unsigned long flags;
69 u32 reg, ctx;
70 int chid;
71
72 if (!nv40_fifo_dma_engine(engine, &reg, &ctx))
73 return 0;
74
75 spin_lock_irqsave(&fifo->base.lock, flags);
76 nvkm_mask(device, 0x002500, 0x00000001, 0x00000000);
77
78 chid = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x003204) & (fifo->base.nr - 1);
79 if (chid == chan->base.chid)
80 nvkm_wr32(device, reg, 0x00000000);
81 nvkm_kmap(imem->ramfc);
82 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + ctx, 0x00000000);
83 nvkm_done(imem->ramfc);
84
85 nvkm_mask(device, 0x002500, 0x00000001, 0x00000001);
86 spin_unlock_irqrestore(&fifo->base.lock, flags);
87 return 0;
88}
89
90static int
91nv40_fifo_dma_engine_init(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base,
92 struct nvkm_engine *engine)
93{
94 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
95 struct nv04_fifo *fifo = chan->fifo;
96 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->base.engine.subdev.device;
97 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = device->imem;
98 unsigned long flags;
99 u32 inst, reg, ctx;
100 int chid;
101
102 if (!nv40_fifo_dma_engine(engine, &reg, &ctx))
103 return 0;
104 inst = chan->engn[engine->subdev.index]->addr >> 4;
105
106 spin_lock_irqsave(&fifo->base.lock, flags);
107 nvkm_mask(device, 0x002500, 0x00000001, 0x00000000);
108
109 chid = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x003204) & (fifo->base.nr - 1);
110 if (chid == chan->base.chid)
111 nvkm_wr32(device, reg, inst);
112 nvkm_kmap(imem->ramfc);
113 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + ctx, inst);
114 nvkm_done(imem->ramfc);
115
116 nvkm_mask(device, 0x002500, 0x00000001, 0x00000001);
117 spin_unlock_irqrestore(&fifo->base.lock, flags);
118 return 0;
119}
120
121static void
122nv40_fifo_dma_engine_dtor(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base,
123 struct nvkm_engine *engine)
124{
125 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
126 nvkm_gpuobj_del(&chan->engn[engine->subdev.index]);
127}
128
129static int
130nv40_fifo_dma_engine_ctor(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base,
131 struct nvkm_engine *engine,
132 struct nvkm_object *object)
133{
134 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
135 const int engn = engine->subdev.index;
136 u32 reg, ctx;
137
138 if (!nv40_fifo_dma_engine(engine, &reg, &ctx))
139 return 0;
140
141 return nvkm_object_bind(object, NULL, 0, &chan->engn[engn]);
142}
143
144static int
145nv40_fifo_dma_object_ctor(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *base,
146 struct nvkm_object *object)
147{
148 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = nv04_fifo_chan(base);
149 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.device->imem;
150 u32 context = chan->base.chid << 23;
151 u32 handle = object->handle;
152 int hash;
153
154 switch (object->engine->subdev.index) {
155 case NVKM_ENGINE_DMAOBJ:
156 case NVKM_ENGINE_SW : context |= 0x00000000; break;
157 case NVKM_ENGINE_GR : context |= 0x00100000; break;
158 case NVKM_ENGINE_MPEG : context |= 0x00200000; break;
159 default:
160 WARN_ON(1);
161 return -EINVAL;
162 }
163
164 mutex_lock(&chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.mutex);
165 hash = nvkm_ramht_insert(imem->ramht, object, chan->base.chid, 4,
166 handle, context);
167 mutex_unlock(&chan->fifo->base.engine.subdev.mutex);
168 return hash;
169}
170
171static const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_func
172nv40_fifo_dma_func = {
173 .dtor = nv04_fifo_dma_dtor,
174 .init = nv04_fifo_dma_init,
175 .fini = nv04_fifo_dma_fini,
176 .engine_ctor = nv40_fifo_dma_engine_ctor,
177 .engine_dtor = nv40_fifo_dma_engine_dtor,
178 .engine_init = nv40_fifo_dma_engine_init,
179 .engine_fini = nv40_fifo_dma_engine_fini,
180 .object_ctor = nv40_fifo_dma_object_ctor,
181 .object_dtor = nv04_fifo_dma_object_dtor,
182};
183
184static int
185nv40_fifo_dma_new(struct nvkm_fifo *base, const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass,
186 void *data, u32 size, struct nvkm_object **pobject)
187{
188 struct nvkm_object *parent = oclass->parent;
189 union {
190 struct nv03_channel_dma_v0 v0;
191 } *args = data;
192 struct nv04_fifo *fifo = nv04_fifo(base);
193 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = NULL;
194 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->base.engine.subdev.device;
195 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = device->imem;
196 int ret;
197
198 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create channel dma size %d\n", size);
199 if (nvif_unpack(args->v0, 0, 0, false)) {
200 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create channel dma vers %d pushbuf %"PRIx64" "
201 "offset %08x\n", args->v0.version,
202 args->v0.pushbuf, args->v0.offset);
203 if (!args->v0.pushbuf)
204 return -EINVAL;
205 } else
206 return ret;
207
208 if (!(chan = kzalloc(sizeof(*chan), GFP_KERNEL)))
209 return -ENOMEM;
210 *pobject = &chan->base.object;
211
212 ret = nvkm_fifo_chan_ctor(&nv40_fifo_dma_func, &fifo->base,
213 0x1000, 0x1000, false, 0, args->v0.pushbuf,
214 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_DMAOBJ) |
215 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_GR) |
216 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_MPEG) |
217 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_SW),
218 0, 0xc00000, 0x1000, oclass, &chan->base);
219 chan->fifo = fifo;
220 if (ret)
221 return ret;
222
223 args->v0.chid = chan->base.chid;
224 chan->ramfc = chan->base.chid * 128;
225
226 nvkm_kmap(imem->ramfc);
227 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x00, args->v0.offset);
228 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x04, args->v0.offset);
229 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x0c, chan->base.push->addr >> 4);
230 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x18, 0x30000000 |
231 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_TRIG_128_BYTES |
232 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_SIZE_128_BYTES |
233#ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN
234 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_BIG_ENDIAN |
235#endif
236 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_MAX_REQS_8);
237 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x3c, 0x0001ffff);
238 nvkm_done(imem->ramfc);
239 return 0;
240}
241
242const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_oclass
243nv40_fifo_dma_oclass = {
244 .base.oclass = NV40_CHANNEL_DMA,
245 .base.minver = 0,
246 .base.maxver = 0,
247 .ctor = nv40_fifo_dma_new,
248};
